    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A small and simple clicker.</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Mine resources, improve the mines, buy upgrades, improve the upgrades</li><li>Earn XP, activate NG+ for even more bonus production</li><li>play <strong><u>EndlessMode</u></strong> and let the numbers grow even higher</li><li>Choose your challenge, <strong><u>the integrated Simple Idle Mods</u></strong> can be activated and combined as desired</li></ul><br>Help Ferdinand Fuchs and the other “important people” to escape.<br>Spoiler alert: He won't be grateful for this.<br>Rather, he will regularly hit you with sayings that range from amusing to borderline offensive.<br><br><br>Ferdinand also loves dressing up.<br>And in every costume he comes with new sayings.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118260/extras/ea3670b506c20acc40cac721fd44f63e.avif?t=1723989379\" width=600 height=108 /></span><br><br>Some more details:<br><br>- 45 achievements wait to get unlocked<br>- &quot;BestPlayed&quot; with mouse, but if you really want to, controllers are supported for the core gameplay.<br><br>Playtime<br>\t- Vanilla: 4-5 hours<br>\t- AllAchievements: +1-2 hours<br>\t<u><strong>-&gt; + EndlessMode; + Mods = X hours extra.</strong></u>",
